headline.print_headline: Rare Michalek Goal Helps Coyotes Beat Penguins 3-1
headline.main: Rare Michalek Goal Helps Coyotes Beat Penguins 3-1

lead_paragraph: Zbynek Michalek scored against his former team, his first goal in 83 games, and the Phoenix Coyotes became the first Pacific Division team to beat the Eastern Conference-leading Pittsburgh Penguins in regulation this season with a 3-1 victory on Saturday night.
